headline: Why The Narrative Around Centene Is Shifting After Analyst Upgrades and New Sector Risks
summary: Centene stock has attracted renewed interest from analysts after its consensus price target increased from $34.63 to $36.00. This marks a modest but notable upward adjustment in fair value expectations. This change comes as investor sentiment balances optimism around earnings visibility and margin recovery with ongoing sector challenges.
